•	Linux/Unix: Master command line, shell scripting (Bash), and system administration.

2. Linux/Unix Fundamentals (लिनक्स की बुनियाद)
क्या सीखें?
•	Command Line Basics: grep, awk, sed, find, ssh, file permissions (chmod, chown).
•	Process Management: ps, top, kill, systemd.
•	Networking Tools: curl, netstat, ping, nslookup.
•	Package Managers: apt, yum, dnf.
कैसे सीखें?
•	Hands-On: अपने PC पर Virtual Machine (VM) में Linux (Ubuntu/CentOS) install करें।
•	Course: Linux Journey (free)।
•	Project: एक Bash script लिखें जो server के RAM और disk usage की report generate करे।
________________________________________
3. Version Control (Git)
क्या सीखें?
•	Git Basics: git clone, commit, push, pull, branch, merge, rebase.
•	Collaboration: GitHub/GitLab पर repositories manage करना, Pull Requests, merge conflicts solve करना।
•	Workflows: Git Flow, Trunk-Based Development।
